as_tibble.krig_lst      Coerce objects of class "krig_lst" to dataframe
                        or tbl (tibble).
krig                    Krige soil data following the methodology of
                        the John et al. (2007).
krig_auto_params        Find "best" variogram parameters.
krig_breaks             Sequence of n exponentially increasing values.
soil_fake               Fake soil data with multiple soil variables.
soil_random             Soil data for examples.
summary.krig_lst        Summary objects of class "krig_lst".
